<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subir Documentos</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- CSS link -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aspirantes/subirDocumentos.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Boton cerrar sesion -->
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-end">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Cerrar Sesión</button>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-center mt-5">SUBIR DOCUMENTOS</h1>
        <hr class="w-50 mx-auto">
        
        <p class="text-center text-muted">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Nibh porta morbi viverra justo mollis. Commodo lacus amet malesuada pretium ac malesuada odio eu donec amet.
            Fermentum lacus semper pellentesque sed. Amet vel lorem sit dui id faucibus. Quis convallis duis at a dolor. 
        </p>

        <!-- Card para subir archivo -->
        <div class="card p-4 mt-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h5 class="card-title">Cargar archivo</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Solo archivos .pdf con menos de 200 kb</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body text-center">
                <div class="border border-secondary rounded p-4">
                    <h6 class="text-muted">Arrastra para subir</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Suelta en este área tu contenido para que se pueda subir</p>
                    <div class="text-center my-2">
                        <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/724/724933.png" alt="Upload icon" width="50">
                    </div>
                    <input class="form-control mt-2" type="file" accept=".pdf" disabled>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center border rounded p-2">
                    <div>
                        <span class="fw-bold">CV.pdf</span>
                        <small class="text-muted">Subiendo (65%)</small>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" disabled>Eliminar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p></p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-color--secondary" >Subir Archivos</button>
        <p></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>